room_title: Escape room "The Mad Scientist" by Code Stat Escape Rooms in Ventura
room_address: 3875 Telegraph Rd Suite D Ventura, CA 93003
room_description: You have suspicions about your colleague, Dr. Astic. After hours, you decide to go snooping around in his lab to see what you can uncover about his nefarious plans. A medical researcher and developer, Dr. Astic may very well have concocted the perfect recipe for human annihilation and escape-room-enthusiast exhilaration.
